this is a project to show how to collect mongodb:
save data
```
node save.js
```
then go mongodb database mongoosedb-demo to check out data
 ```
 use mongoosedb-demo
 show collections
 db.users.find()
 ```
find data
```
node find.js
```
then go mongodb database mongoosedb-demo to check out data
 ```
 use mongoosedb-demo
 show collections
 db.users.find()
 ```
update data
```
node update.js
```
then go mongodb database mongoosedb-demo to check out data
 ```
 use mongoosedb-demo
 show collections
 db.users.find()
 ```
delete data
```
node remove.js
```
then go mongodb database mongoosedb-demo to check out data
 ```
 use mongoosedb-demo
 show collections
 db.users.find()
 ```

